						               													<description>Ready, Set, Roll! It's a different way to play the Clue game! Unlike the classic Clue game, this Diced edition has no gameboard and players roll to find out whodunit. This fun game has players rolling the Suspect dice and the Bonus die, getting closer to guessing the culprit as opponents reveal their cards. When a player is ready to crack the case, they secretly look at the cards placed inside the Case File envelope to reveal who was the brains and who was the brawn behind the crime. The Clue Diced game is a compact and portable game making it a great game for travel and for on-the-go play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Put simply: Instead of moving pawns around the board and making a guess in a room (as in classic Clue), players simply roll 4 dice and pick a combination of people and roles to gain information about.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Includes 2 levels of difficulty.&amp;#10;Includes game case, 18 suspect cards, 4 dice, dice labels, case file envelope, suggestion board, detective pad, and game rules.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
